 <body>
  <p>The main steps of the execution process are (example: cart abandonment):</p> 
  <ol>
   <li><p>A client adds a product to their cart.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Adobe Analytics detects this behavior and, after a period of inactivity (up to 4 hours maximum), Adobe Marketing Cloud sends an event to Adobe Campaign.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Adobe Campaign receives the event.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Adobe Campaign reconciles the event with a profile to recover the email address. The event is then stored in the database.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Adobe Campaign sends the personalized transactional message associated with the client.</p> </li>
  </ol>
